# 📝 Private-CV-Maker

A professional, high-performance web application designed to generate professional CVs/Resumes while prioritizing absolute user privacy.

### ✨ Key Features:
- **100% Privacy-First:** No personal data is ever stored on a database or sent to any external server.
- **Client-Side Generation:** All PDF processing happens locally in your browser.
- **Instant PDF Download:** Generate a clean, formatted PDF with a single click.
- **Minimalist Design:** A clean and responsive interface for a smooth user experience.

### 🛠️ Tech Stack:
- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3 (Custom Styles)
- **Logic:** Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)
- **Library:** [jsPDF](https://github.com/parallax/jsPDF) for high-quality document generation.

### 🚀 How to Use:
1. Open the application in your browser.
2. Fill in your professional details (Name, Skills, Experience).
3. Click "Generate PDF" to download your ready-to-use resume instantly.

